AB  - Universal method for process analysis using LLM-powered extraction and Mermaid visualization. Domain-agnostic methodology demonstrated across biology (100+ processes), chemistry, mathematics, physics, and computer science. Converts textual process descriptions into structured, computable diagrammatic representations.
